imated influence of varying line-of-sight\nparticle densities on the magnetic field strength derived from observed\nrotation measures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Jan 2009 16:15:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-02-11"}
