ps, the dihedral group $D_{2n}$ with even $n$,\nthe Clifford group CL(n) and all of the $p$-groups can be achieved.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Jan 2009 17:15:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 Mar 2009 14:53:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-29"}
